title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You could derive immense gratification from performing a charitable service or helping a stranger now. But whatever you decide to do must be from the heart while sweet Venus visits your 12th House of Soul Consciousness, and not from an obligation to look good or for reciprocal benefit. Acting from pure intentions in one area of your life possibly goads you to check whether you are as generous and caring in other relationships as well. Releasing more love into the world without strings attached not only helps you feel free, but others too. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
